4. Music and Sounds
The music and sounds in this project are all licensed under the Creative Commons. Some of these pieces require attribution. All songs by Kevin MacLeod were found at his brilliant site http://incompetech.com/. Below is a list of all applications and their attributions:
GNMS Air Hockey:  All sound effects performed by Larry Price
GNMS Calibrate:   All sound effects found on FreeSound.com
GNMS Matching:    Intractable       by Kevin MacLeod
GNMS Paint:       Wallpaper         by Kevin MacLeod
     	          Airport Lounge    by Kevin MacLeod
	          Modern Jazz Samba by Kevin MacLeod
GNMS Roulette:    All sound effects found on FreeSound.com
GNMS Tic-Tac-Toe: Artifact          by Kevin MacLeod

